text:
Seeking help trying to get a module to inherit the styles it's nested within. Here's my code. I want that inline_rich_text to inherit the style from the p tag above it, but it does not. Any thoughts?
``` &lt;td align="left" style="font-size:0px;padding:20px 35px;padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:0px;word-break:break-word;"&gt;
                                &lt;div style="font-family:'Roboto', sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:180%;text-align:left;color:#000000;"&gt;
                                  &lt;p style="padding-top:0px!important;margin-top:0px!important"&gt;
                               {% inline_rich_text field="lead_story_body" value="{{ module.lead_story_body }}" %}
                                  &lt;/p&gt;
                                &lt;/div&gt;
                              &lt;/td&gt;```
